&lt;li id=&#34;fn1&#34;&gt;&lt;p&gt;I’m using mainly R with RStudio, but I have some basic experience with Stata, Systat, GeoDa, Qgis, Markdown, Rmarkdown, LaTex and I’m intentioned to learn Python.&lt;a href=&#34;#fnref1&#34;&gt;↩&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li id=&#34;fn2&#34;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.r-project.org/&#34;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt; is a a free software environment for statistical computing and graphics and &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.rstudio.com&#34;&gt;Rstudio&lt;/a&gt; is an integrated development environment (IDE) for R.&lt;a href=&#34;#fnref2&#34;&gt;↩&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
